@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 场景：地面站控制单台 UGV 的协议协作时序
hide footbox

actor "Ground Station" as GS
participant "UGV Runtime" as UGV #EEF2F4
participant "Drive Executor" as DRV #F1F4F6

== Session ==
GS -> UGV : SessionHello / Authenticate /\nCapabilities / Ready
UGV --> GS : Session 本地推进到 Active

== Authority ==
GS -> UGV : AuthorityRequest(action=Claim)\ntarget = Entity(UGV#21)
UGV --> GS : AuthorityStatus(state=Controller)\n或本地租约已生效

== Continuous Control ==
loop short-TTL control window
  GS -> UGV : Command.VelocitySetpoint\nbody_frame + short ttl_ms
  UGV --> GS : CommandResult.Received
  UGV --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted
end

== Trajectory Extension ==
opt 需要轨迹分块时
  GS -> UGV : Command.TrajectoryChunk
  UGV --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted
end

== Uplink ==
UGV -> DRV : 执行速度或轨迹
DRV --> UGV : 状态变化 / 故障
UGV --> GS : StateSnapshot.VehicleCore
UGV --> GS : StateEvent.VehicleEvent(kind=Fault) (optional)

note right of UGV
UGV 场景的特殊点不是图种不同，
而是“连续控制 + 短 TTL”必须被看出来。
end note
@enduml
